Class GenericPoint

java.lang.Object
org.ivoa.dm.stc.coords.Coordinate

All Implemented Interfaces:
org.ivoa.vodml.jpa.JPAManipulations
@Embeddable @VoDml(id="coords:GenericPoint", role=dataType) public class GenericPoint extends Point implements org.ivoa.vodml.jpa.JPAManipulations
GenericPoint supports the representation of spatial coordinates in a custom coordinate space, or any space which is not covered by the other specializations. The coordinate values map, in order, to the axes described by the associated CoordSpace. If no CoordSpace is provided, the behavior is undefined. Values for unused/undefined dimensions need not be provided. dataType: GenericPoint
